verbose_text: In Figure XREF_FIG different variants of MP2 are also shown, and a comparison of the performance of MP2 (full OS part, full same-spin (SS) contribution) and SOS-MP2 (no SS part) underlines the unfavorable effect of the SS correlation if evaluated perturbatively (MAD (SOS-MP2) = 9.3 kcal mol -1, MAD (MP2) = 14.9 kcal mol -1).
evidence: SOS-MP2 (no SS part) underlines the unfavorable effect of the SS
